\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Applied a modern color palette, improved typography, and clean spacing across the page.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added high-quality images and icons to enhance visual appeal.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured consistent styling that matches the project’s theme and branding.</li></ol><h4>? 3. Mobile Responsiveness</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Made the entire home page fully responsive for mobile, tablet, and desktop.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Adjusted alignment, spacing, and scaling to ensure smooth viewing across all devices.</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>Today’s work delivered a polished and functional <strong>Home Page</strong> for the Ihumure System, featuring:</p><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? A clean and structured design</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>?️ Improved visuals and user experience</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Full responsiveness across screen sizes</li></ol><p>This update sets a strong foundation for building the rest of the frontend pages in the Ihumure System.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-24 21:58:00.000','6a8aa455-94f0-4e98-92e7-809c64adcfe4'),('6f0606b7-4cb9-4516-a6e4-137dccc7b22d','Clarification, Debugging & System Optimization (Analytical & Technical Style)','\"\\\"<p><strong>Today I worked on</strong> clarifying system requirements and performing multiple rounds of debugging across backend and frontend components.</p><h3><strong>Introduction</strong></h3><p>The focus of today’s activities was to resolve unclear system behaviors and to address defects identified in both backend services and frontend interfaces. This also included evaluating the system’s vulnerability exposure, reviewing performance bottlenecks, and aligning the product more closely with user-experience expectations.</p><h3><strong>Body of the Report</strong></h3><p>I began by gathering and organizing clarification notes related to user flows, data-handling expectations, and notification interactions. After clarifying these points, I proceeded with debugging API inconsistencies that caused intermittent failures in the booking and status-retrieval processes. On the frontend, I analyzed the rendering speed and optimized several components by reducing redundant state updates.</p><p> To ensure system robustness, I ran basic vulnerability checks and inspected slow database queries to identify areas needing optimization. I also evaluated the overall UX, focusing on navigation efficiency and responsiveness.</p><h3><strong>Challenges Encountered</strong></h3><p>Some endpoints exhibited unpredictable delays, making it difficult to determine whether the root cause was the database or the middleware. Additionally, several frontend components were tightly coupled, which made debugging more time-consuming.</p><h3><strong>How the Challenges Were Fixed</strong></h3><p>I added diagnostic logs to the backend, which exposed a batch of queries running without indexing—these were optimized and re-indexed. On the frontend, I separated a few large components into smaller, reusable ones to reduce complexity and improve state handling. Vulnerability warnings were mitigated by adjusting outdated dependencies and fixing permission checks within middleware.</p><h3><strong>Why This Approach Was Chosen</strong></h3><p>A diagnostic-first method allowed the most accurate identification of root causes, ensuring fixes were targeted rather than speculative. Refactoring and indexing were chosen because they provide long-term stability, improve maintainability, and reduce performance regressions.</p><h3><strong>Conclusion</strong></h3><p>The system now runs with fewer delays, improved clarity in behavior, and stronger protection against vulnerabilities. These changes also contribute to a more intuitive experience for users interacting with the platform.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-17 21:23:00.000','6a8aa455-94f0-4e98-92e7-809c64adcfe4'),('6f899693-ae32-4580-976f-b92298a28f37','? Aby Inventory – Responsiveness Improvement Report','\"\\\"<p><br></p><h1>? <strong>Aby Inventory – Responsiveness Improvement Report</strong></h1><p><strong>Name:</strong> Mihigo Honore</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on improving the <strong>responsiveness of the Aby Inventory system</strong>. The main goal was to ensure the interface works smoothly and displays correctly across different screen sizes and devices.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? 1. Layout &amp; Grid Adjustments</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Refined page layouts to adapt properly on desktop, tablet, and mobile screens.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Fixed alignment and overflow issues in tables and forms.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved grid and flex behavior to maintain consistency across breakpoints.</li></ol><h4>? 2. UI Element Optimization</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Adjusted font sizes, padding, and margins for better readability on smaller screens.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured buttons, inputs, and action icons resize and reposition correctly.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved usability of tables and filters on mobile devices.</li></ol><h4>? 3. Testing &amp; Refinement</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Tested the inventory pages on multiple screen sizes.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Fixed responsiveness bugs causing layout breaks or hidden content.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured a smooth and consistent user experience across all devices.</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>Today’s work improved the <strong>Aby Inventory</strong> system by making it:</p><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Fully responsive</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Easier to use on small screens</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? More stable across devices</li></ol><p>These improvements enhance accessibility and usability for all users managing inventory.</p><p><br></p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-29 20:12:00.000','f8cab911-6027-445b-995d-a4b94efd8e00'),('7131763a-51c0-4931-842a-f0c353e420a3','? UI Cleanup & Frontend Improvements – Daily Work Progress Report','\"\\\"<h1>? <strong>UI Cleanup &amp; Frontend Improvements – Daily Work Progress Report</strong></h1><p><strong>Name:</strong> Shema Serge</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I focused on improving the frontend experience across diffe