stem runs correctly</strong> by testing different features and validating overall functionality. The focus was on confirming that recent changes work as expected and that the system remains stable.</p><h3>✅ Work Done</h3><h4>? System Testing</h4><p>Ran tests on key system features to ensure they function correctly.</p><p> Verified that recent updates did not break existing functionality.</p><p> Checked data flow between frontend and backend to confirm everything works smoothly.</p><h4>? Validation &amp; Issue Checking</h4><p>Reviewed system behavior to identify any unexpected issues.</p><p> Confirmed that fixes and new features operate correctly under normal use.</p><p> Reported and noted any issues that require further attention.</p><h3>? Impact</h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved confidence in system stability</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Reduced risk of errors in production</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Better reliability of recent features</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>This work focused on testing and validating the system to ensure everything runs properly and is ready for continued development and use.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-27 23:06:00.000','8f2850d4-4182-454c-bf0e-2eca4a700fc0'),('764fff3c-6966-4c15-ab44-140baf58eb35','? Daily Work Progress Report','\"\\\"<h1>? Daily Work Progress Report</h1><p><strong>Name:</strong> Shema Serge</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on improving the user interface of <strong>Aby Dash</strong>, focusing specifically on the design of the menu items to make the system cleaner, modern, and easier to navigate.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? 1. Redesigned Menu Item Layout</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span cla