-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Resolved cases where some orders were being saved without key fields.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved backend validation to catch errors early.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured every order has complete, accurate data before being stored.</li></ol><h3>? <strong>3. Improved Error Feedback in the UI</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Made error messages clearer and more visible.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured users understand exactly what needs to be corrected.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Reduced confusion and improved the overall flow of creating an order.</li></ol><h3>? <strong>4. System Cleanup &amp; Stability Enhancements</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Removed outdated validation logic.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Cleaned unused functions and improved overall code readability.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Increased system stability during high activity or rapid input.</li></ol><h2>? <strong>Summary</strong></h2><p>The order section now includes:</p><p>? Stronger validation rules</p><p> ? Accurate and complete data saving</p><p> ? Clear user feedback when errors occur</p><p> ? A cleaner and more stable codebase</p><p>These improvements make the order process mo