perform in terms of popularity, profitability, and cost. The goal was to support better menu decisions using clear and reliable data.</p><h3>✅ Work Done</h3><h4>? Item Popularity Ranking</h4><p>Worked on logic and views that rank menu items based on how often they are ordered.</p><p>Ensured popularity data is clear and easy to compare across items.</p><h4>? Profitability by Dish</h4><p>Implemented support for showing profitability per dish by combining cost and revenue data.</p><p>Helped highlight high-performing and low-performing menu items.</p><h4>? Menu Engineering Insights</h4><p>Prepared analysis views that support <strong>menu engineering</strong>, helping identify stars, puzzles, plow-horses, and dogs.</p><p>Structured data to make strategic menu decisions easier.</p><h4>? Underperforming Item Detection</h4><p>Worked on identifying menu items that perform poorly in terms of sales or profit.</p><p>Ensured underperforming items are clearly flagged for review.</p><h4>? Recipe Cost Analysis</h4><p>Supported analysis of <strong>recipe and ingredient costs</strong> per menu item.</p><p>Helped connect ingredient usage and cost data to menu performance insights.</p><h3>? Impact</h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Clear understanding of menu item performance</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Better insight into profitability and cost per dish</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Strong support for data-driven menu decisions</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>This work improved Aby Dash menu performance analysis by providing clear insights into item popularity, profitability, costs, and underperforming items, helping businesses optimize their menus effectively.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-02-03 18:51:00.000','8f2850d4-4182-454c-bf0e-2eca4a700fc0'),('a3876a58-46be-4c5c-913d-7cd7c6bda40d','Technical & Operational Assessment of Stock and Reporting Modules','\"\\\"<h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><p>This document outlines an assessment of the stock management processes and summarizes recent work carried out on backend and frontend system components, with emphasis on stability, performance, and usability.</p><h2><strong>Body</strong></h2><h3><strong>Stock Management</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Real-time monitoring active</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Stock audit trail expanded</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Low-quantity alerts recalibrated</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Product metadata updated for accuracy</li></ol><h3><strong>Reporting Management</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added automated scheduled reports</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved graph rendering</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Optimized database queries for faster summaries</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Enhanced user filters for custom reporting</li></ol><h3><strong>Backend Work</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Refactoring of stock controllers</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Database indexing improved</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added role-based authorization checks</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Enhanced data validation rules</li></ol><h3><strong>Frontend Work</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Integrated live data refresh</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved input error highlights</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added collapsible report sections</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Updated component structure for better maintainability</li></ol><h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2><p>The system demonstrates measurable improvement in performance, reliability, and user interaction. Continued enhancements, especially in automation and analytics, will further strengthen overall system efficiency.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-20 21:41:00.000','f8cab911-6027-445b-995d-a4b94efd8e00'),('a3f9042e-5d14-4652-a219-6e503a2ccc7a','Managing Reporting System and Forum Website – Overview','\"\\\"<p>The management of a reporting system and forum website requires careful coordination to ensure both data integrity and user engagement. Efficient systems allow user issues to be addressed promptly while creating a safe and interactive online environment. This report outlines strategies for handling reports, moderating forums, enhancing user experience, and maintaining system reliability.</p><h3><br></h3><p><strong>1. Reporting System Management</strong></p><p> A reporting system enables users to submit issues, feedback, or complaints in a structured manner. Effective management includes monitoring incoming reports, categorizing them, and prioritizing urgent matters. Regular analysis of reports helps identify recurring problems, allowing improvements to system efficiency and response times.</p><p><strong>2. Forum Management</strong></p><p> The forum website aims to foster meaningful discussions while upholding community guidelines. Moderation is essential to remove inappropriate content promptly. Organizing content into categories and subforums enhances navigation, enabling users to find relevant discussions easily. Features such as search functions, notifications, and user profiles further improve interactivity and engagement.</p><p><strong>3. Integration and Workflow</strong></p><p> Linking the reporting system with forum operations streamlines workflow. For instance, flagged forum posts can automatically trigger alerts for moderators. Maintaining a dashboard to track report status ensures transparency and accountability. Regular updates and feedback loops with users further enhance system reliability and performance.</p><h3><strong>Conclusion</strong></h3><p>By implementing these strategies, administrators can effectively manage both reporting systems and forum websites. Combining structured reporting with organized forum management ensures timely issue resolution, improved user satisfaction, and an efficient, engaging online community.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-23 14:02:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('a45021c9-e4f7-47a5-b0e9-127c30903476','Final Project Report: Amis de la Paix and Engineer for Humanity Websites','\"\\\"<p>Work related to identifying solutions and completing the remaining tasks for the Amis de la Paix website and the Engineer for Humanity website has now been finalized. Both platforms have been reviewed, corrected where necessary, and confirmed to be functioning correctly.</p><p>The websites are ready for use in their current state. All core features are active, and no further engineering work is required. The focus now shifts exclusively to content accuracy, as only real and officially approved data needs to be uploaded.</p><h3><br></h3><p>The project has reached completion from a technical standpoint. Once real data is added, both websites will be fully ready for official operation and long-term use.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-29 14:48:00.000','8f2850d4-4182-454c-bf0e-2eca4a700fc0'),('a66169eb-73bb-46cb-b888-60f6345bcb4a','? E4H Initiative – About Page Real Data Integration Report','\"\\\"<p><br></p><h1>? <strong>E4H Initiative – About Page Real Data Integration Report</strong></h1><p><strong>Name:</strong> Mihigo Prince</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on the <strong>About Page</strong> of the <strong>Engineering 4 Human (E4H)</strong> website. The main objective was to replace placeholder content with real, meaningful data that accurately represents the organization’s identity, mission, and long-term vision.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? 1. Integrated Real Organizational Information</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Replaced all dummy text with real descriptions about E4H.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Updated sections such as <em>Who We Are</em>, <em>Our Mission</em>, <em>Our Vision</em>, and <em>Our Values</em>.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured all content reflects the true purpose and goals of the organization.</li></ol><h4>? 2. Added Authentic Project &amp; Initiative Details</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Included accurate information about ongoing community programs and engineering projects.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Updated milestone highlights and impact points based on real accomplishments.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured content aligns with E4H’s current focus and future plans.</li></ol><h4>? 3. Improved Page Layout for Clarity</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Adjusted spacing and typography to align with the updated real data.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Enhanced visual hierarchy to make important information easier to read.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured that updated sections blend smoothly with the existing design style.</li></ol><h4>? 4. Mobile &amp; Desktop Optimization</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Made responsive adjustments to ensure longer, real descriptions display properly.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Fixed layout shifts caused by additional content on smaller screens.</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>Today’s updates made the E4H About Page more professional and authentic by:</p><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Integrating accurate real-world content</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Highlighting true projects and initiatives</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Improving structure and readability</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Ensuring full responsiveness on all devices</li></ol><p>These changes help visitors clearly understand what Engineering 4 Human stands for and the real impact it brings.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-26 19:01:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('a69815b6-901b-4cca-b06b-98193f4a1cca','? Engineer 4 Humanity – Homepage Data Update Report','\"\\\"<p>\\\\\\\"</p><h1><strong>? Engineer 4 Humanity – Homepage Data Update Report</strong></h1><p><strong>Name</strong>: Mihigo Honore</p><p><strong>Position</strong>: Frontend Developer</p><p><strong>Date</strong>: 29 November 2025</p><p>? <strong>Introduction</strong></p><p>Today, I updated the Engineer 4 Humanity homepage by modifying key data and content sections. The goal was to ensure that all information displayed is accurate, relevant, and visually consistent, providing users with a clear and engaging experience.</p><p>✅ <strong>Key Tasks Completed</strong></p><p>? <strong>1. Updated Homepage Data</strong></p><p>Replaced outdated or placeholder data with accurate and real information.</p><p>Ensured that statistics, numbers, and textual content reflect the latest updates.</p><p>Verified that all sections convey the intended message clearly.</p><p>? <strong>2. Layout and Design Adjustments</strong></p><p>Refined spacing, typography, and alignment to match the overall homepage design.</p><p>Ensured a clean and modern visual appearance consistent with the brand.</p><p>Improved readability and emphasis on key data points.</p><p>?️ <strong>3. UI/UX Enhancements</strong></p><p>Polished interactive elements and visual cues to guide users effectively.</p><p>Ensured that all updated data is visually prominent and easy to understand.</p><p>Maintained consistency with the overall theme and user experience standards.</p><p>? <strong>4. Full Responsiveness Checks</strong></p><p>Tested the homepage across mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.</p><p>Fixed layout and alignment issues to ensure smooth scaling and readability.</p><p>? <strong>Summary</strong></p><p>The Engineer 4 Humanity homepage now features:</p><p>? Accurate and updated data</p><p>? Polished layout and design</p><p>?️ Improved UI/UX for better clarity and engagement</p><p>? Fully responsive interface</p><p>These updates provide users with a professional, accurate, and engaging homepage experience.</p><p>\\\\\\\"</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-28 18:20:00.000','f8cab911-6027-445b-995d-a4b94efd8e00'),('a8579ea3-4e9d-4dd3-b3e1-2b94556041f0','E4H Initiative – Donors Page & Apply Page Development Report','\"\\\"<h1><strong>E4H Initiative – Donors Page &amp; Apply Page Development Report</strong></h1><p><strong>Name:</strong> Shema Serge</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on improving and expanding the <strong>Donors Page</strong> and the <strong>Apply Page</strong> for the <strong>Engineering 4 Human (E4H)</strong> website. The goal was to make it easier for supporters to understand how to contribute and for applicants to submit their information smoothly.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? 1. Donors Page Development</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Designed a clean and organized layout that highlights the importance of donors.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added sections explaining how donations support E4H programs and community projects.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Included areas for donor categories, contribution options, and impact information.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved visual structure to make the page more engaging and trustworthy.</li></ol><h4>? 2. Apply Page Implementation</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Created the <strong>Apply Page</strong> where users can submit their details to join or support E4H programs.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added well-structured input fields such as name, email, phone number, and purpose of application.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured the form layout is clear, responsive, and easy to complete.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Prepared the page for backend integration to process submissions.</li></ol><h4>? 3. Full Responsiveness</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured both pages work smoothly on mobile, tablet, and desktop.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Adjusted spacing and alignment to keep the UI clean on smaller screens.</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>Today\'s work improved two important sections of the E4H platform:</p><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Professional and informative <strong>Donors Page</strong></li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? User-friendly <strong>Apply Page</strong></li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Full responsiveness across all devices</li></ol><p>These updates make it easier for donors to support E4H and for applicants to engage directly with the initiative.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-26 19:37:00.000','8f2850d4-4182-454c-bf0e-2eca4a700fc0'),('a99298a5-2183-4346-81b6-0993fd4ca7d8','? Order Stock Reduction Fix & Deployment Report','\"\\\"<h2>? Order Stock Reduction Fix &amp; Deployment Report</h2><p><strong>Name:</strong> Mihigo Prince</p><h3>? Overview</h3><p>I worked on fixing a <strong>critical stock reduction issue</strong> that occurred during order processing. The problem happened when an order was completed, stock was reduced, and then new items were added to the same order. In that case, the system could not correctly identify which items had already been reduced, leading to incorrect stock handling. After fixing this, I also <strong>deployed the solution to production</strong>.</p><h3>✅ Work Done</h3><h4>?️ Stock Reduction Logic Fix</h4><p>Identified the issue where previously reduced items were not being tracked correctly.</p><p>Updated the order logic to clearly determine <strong>which items have already been reduced</strong> from stock.</p><p>Ensured that when new items are added after stock reduction, only the <strong>new items</strong> are reduced, avoiding double reduction or missed deductions.</p><h4>⚙️ Deployment to Production</h4><p>Deployed the fixed stock reduction logic to the production environment.</p><p>Verified that the fix works correctly in the live system.</p><p>Ensured no existing order or stock data was affected by the update.</p><h3>? Impact</h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Accurate stock reduction even when orders are updated</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Prevention of double stock reduction or missed deductions</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Stable and reliable behavior in production</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>This work resolved a complex order stock reduction issue and ensured the fix was safely deployed to production, improving inventory accuracy and system reliability.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-02-02 19:56:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('a9df2bc9-86d4-4479-9fce-b845bd593080','? Employee Expense Permission Report','\"\\\"<h2>? Employee Expense Permission Report</h2><p><strong>Name:</strong> Mihigo Prince</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on managing <strong>employee permissions</strong> related to expenses in the system to improve control and accountability.</p><h3>✅ Work Done</h3><h4>? <strong>Expense Permission Management</strong></h4><p>Configured permissions to allow employees to <strong>add expenses</strong>.</p><p>Enabled authorized employees to <strong>edit existing expense records</strong>.</p><p>Allowed permitted users to <strong>delete expenses</strong> when necessary.</p><h4>? <strong>Result</strong></h4><p>Proper role-based access for expense management.</p><p>Improved security and control over expense data.</p><p>Reduced errors and unauthorized changes.</p><h3>? Summary</h3><p>This task ensured that employees with the right permissions can add, edit, and delete expenses efficiently while maintaining proper system control.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-20 20:04:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('b2ec9c07-7508-4347-b129-23a36e1379a8','? Aby Dash – Financial Reports Backend','\"\\\"<h2>? Aby Dash – Financial Reports Backend</h2><p><strong>Name:</strong> Mihigo Prince</p><h3>? Overview</h3><p>I worked on the <strong>financial reports feature</strong>, focusing on backend logic that automatically generates structured financial insights. The aim was to make financial reporting reliable, detailed, and easy to use for business analysis and decision-making.</p><h3>✅ Work Done</h3><h4>? Financial Summaries</h4><p>Implemented backend logic to automatically generate <strong>daily, weekly, and monthly financial summaries</strong>.</p><p>Ensured summaries accurately reflect sales, expenses, and overall financial performance.</p><h4>? Expense Breakdown</h4><p>Developed backend processes to categorize and break down expenses clearly.</p><p>Made it easy to understand where money is being spent across different expense types.</p><h4>? Profit Margins by Menu Item</h4><p>Worked on calculating <strong>profit margins per menu item</strong> by combining cost and revenue data.</p><p>Ensured results are accurate and consistent for reporting purposes.</p><h4>? Cost Analysis &amp; Recommendations</h4><p>Implemented backend logic to analyze costs in relation to revenue.</p><p>Prepared data structures that support insights and recommendations for improving profitability.</p><h3>? Impact</h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Automated and reliable financial reporting</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Clear visibility into expenses and profit margins</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Better financial insight to support informed decisions</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>This work enhanced Aby Dash financial reporting by enabling automatic generation of summaries, expense breakdowns, profit margins by menu item, and cost analysis, providing strong backend support for financial insights.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-02-03 18:45:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('b645d12f-4896-495b-bea3-8043745d368e','? Aby Inventory Debt Recording Frontend Updates','\"\\\"<h2><strong>? Aby Inventory Debt Recording Frontend Updates</strong></h2><p><strong>Name:</strong> Prince Mihigo</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on the <strong>Aby Inventory System</strong>, focusing on the <strong>frontend updates for debt recording</strong>. The goal was to allow users to <strong>record debts directly from the stock-out page</strong> and to <strong>display debt information on the dashboard</strong> for easy tracking and management.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? <strong>Updating Stock-Out Page</strong></h4><p>Modified the stock-out page to include fields for recording debts.</p><p> Ensured that users can input debt details when adding stock-out entries.</p><p> Implemented validations to prevent missing or incorrect debt information.</p><p> Improved the user interface for a smooth and intuitive debt entry experience.</p><h4>? <strong>Dashboard Debt Display</strong></h4><p>Updated the dashboard to show debt records and summaries.</p><p> Created visual indicators for outstanding debts for quick reference.</p><p> Ensured that debt data updates in real-time as stock-out entries are added.</p><h3>? Summary</h3><p>Today’s work enhanced the Aby Inventory frontend:</p><p>? <strong>Stock-Out Debt Entry:</strong> Users can now record debts directly during stock-out.</p><p> ? <strong>Debt Dashboard:</strong> Debt information is clearly visible and easy to track.</p><p> ⚙️ <strong>Improved UX:</strong> Frontend updates make debt recording and monitoring more intuitive.</p><p>These updates make it easier for users to manage debts and monitor outstanding stock-out balances directly from the frontend.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-09 14:50:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('b737b054-2b61-4785-a62f-83f58438f25f','? Chat Application Message Management Report','\"\\\"<h2>? Chat Application Message Management Report</h2><p><strong>Name:</strong> Shema Serge</p><h3>? Report Overview</h3><p>I worked on improving the <strong>chat application</strong> by adding key message management features that give users more control over their conversa