er</p><p> Date: 29 November 2025</p><p>? <strong>Introduction</strong></p><p>Today, I completed several improvements on the menu item management section of the Aby Dash system. The updates focused on fixing issues, improving usability, reducing unnecessary scrolling, and adding automatic profit/loss visibility when creating or editing menu items.</p><p>✅ <strong>Key Tasks Completed</strong></p><p>?️ <strong>1. Fixed Menu Item Issues</strong></p><p>Resolved bugs affecting how menu items were being displayed or edited.</p><p> Ensured all fields load correctly and respond without lag.</p><p> Improved the stability of the menu item workflow.</p><p>? <strong>2. Redesigned the Create Page for Better Usability</strong></p><p>Reorganized form fields to make the page more user-friendly.</p><p> Reduced excessive scrolling by grouping related fields together.</p><p> Made the layout cleaner and easier for staff to navigate.</p><p>? <strong>3. Added Automatic Profit/Loss Calculation Display</strong></p><p>Implemented a feature that instantly shows profit or loss based on item cost and selling price.</p><p> Ensured calculations update live as the user types.</p><p> Improved clarity so staff can make better pricing decisions.</p><p>? <strong>4. UI/UX Enhancements</strong></p><p>Improved spacing, alignment, and text readability across the page.</p><p> Ensured interactive elements are clear and easy to understand.</p><p> Made the overall experience smoother and more intuitive.</p><p>? <strong>5. Responsiveness &amp; Testing</strong></p><p>Tested the updated page on mobile, tablet, and desktop.</p><p> Ensured all fields, calculations, and layouts scale properly.</p><p> Fixed alignment issues for a consistent user experience.</p><p>? <strong>Summary</strong></p><p>The menu item section now features:</p><p>?️ Fixed functionality issues</p><p> ? A cleaner and more user-friendly create page</p><p> ? Live profit/loss visibility</p><p> ? Improved UI/UX design</p><p> ? Full responsiveness</p><p>These updates make managing menu items faster, clearer, and more efficient for Aby Dash users.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-29 20:26:00.000','8f2850d4-4182-454c-bf0e-2eca4a700fc0'),('d9ea27c4-50c0-4ca9-9a08-ed720022f3a0','? Receipt Card Price Display Improvement Report','\"\\\"<h2>? Receipt Card Price Display Improvement Report</h2><p><strong>Name:</strong> Ishimwe Serge</p><h3>? Overview</h3><p>I worked on improving the way prices are displayed on receipt cards to make them clearer and more informative for users. The main focus was to fix the issue where receipts were not showing detailed pricing when multiple items were printed.</p><h3>✅ Detailed Work Done</h3><h4>? Improved Receipt Price Visibility</h4><p>I updated the receipt card structure and display logic so that prices are shown more clearly. Previously, when multiple items were printed, the receipt only displayed the total amount, which made it difficult to understand how that total was calculated.</p><h4>? Displaying Individual Item Prices</h4><p>The receipt now shows the <strong>price of each printed item</strong>, instead of only the combined total. This allows users to see exactly how much each item costs, improving transparency and accuracy.</p><h4>?️ Better Receipt Output</h4><p>I ensured the layout remains clean and readable even when many items are printed. Prices are properly aligned and easy to follow, making the receipt more professional and user-friendly.</p><h3>? Impact</h3><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Clear visibility of prices for all printed items</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Easier verification of charges</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Reduced confusion for customers and staff</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>More professional and reliable receipt output</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>This improvement enhanced the receipt system by ensuring that all item prices are displayed clearly on receipt cards. It provides better transparency, improves user trust, and makes the overall billing process easier to understand and verify.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-20 19:08:00.000','6a8aa455-94f0-4e98-92e7-809c64adcfe4'),('da7da211-7f18-4c8f-8d7e-a7075782df95','? Daily Work Progress Report','\"\\\"<h1>? Daily Work Progress Report</h1><p><strong>Name:</strong> Ishimwe Serge</p><p> <strong>Position:</strong> Full Stack Developer</p><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I worked on the <strong>Push Notification System</strong> for the Aby Booking web platform. The main goal was to enable users to receive important notifications <strong>even when the web app is closed</strong>, improving communication, responsiveness, and real-time updates.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? 1. Push Notification Setup</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Integrated <strong>Push Notifications</strong> into the Aby Booking web application.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Implemented service workers to handle notifications in the background, allowing alerts to appear even when the app is not open.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Set up browser permissions so users can allow or block notifications based on their preferences.</li></ol><h4>? 2. Background Notification Handling</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured the system can deliver notifications <strong>without requiring the user to be active on the website</strong>.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Configured background processes to receive push messages from the server.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Tested notification delivery across different browsers to ensure consistency.</li></ol><h4>? 3. Server Integration</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Connected the push system with the backend so servers can send messages directly to users’ devices.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added secure token handling to identify the right user when sending notifications.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Created basic API endpoints for sending and managing push messages.</li></ol><h3>? Summary</h3><p>Today’s updates bring a major enhancement to <strong>Aby Booking</strong>:</p><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Users can now <strong>receive push notifications even when the app is closed</strong>.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Background notification handling ensures important updates never get missed.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>? Full backend integration allows automated or manual push messages to be sent anytime.</li></ol><p>This makes Aby Booking more responsive and reliable, keeping users updated in real time regardless of whether the web app is open.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-15 19:44:0