/p><p>This setup lays the groundwork for building stable, secure, and scalable backend features for the platform.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-01 20:53:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('dd86e33a-b7b8-489f-bca8-d16318187586','today\'s progress on abydash',NULL,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dfavs66eh/raw/upload/v1762902481/abytech/report/dssdfyppsex1srtwxumw.pdf','abytech/report/dssdfyppsex1srtwxumw.pdf','2025-11-11 19:12:00.000','ae4f5b82-fda2-4fb1-90fa-e94efc468605'),('ddabb037-0264-4ec9-8269-17a5ac4b0037','Operational Note on Stock Flow and System Stability','\"\\\"<h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><p>This note presents the current standing of stock-related tasks, reporting improvements, and technical corrections applied to address notification inconsistencies experienced on certain production devices.</p><h2><strong>Body</strong></h2><p>Stock flow records have been updated to ensure greater transparency. The checking process was revised, and product quantities now reflect real-time values with fewer discrepancies. The intake and delivery steps were also reviewed to reduce delays.</p><p>The reporting suite received several adjustments. Calculation accuracy for totals has been refined, and the rendering logic for long reports has been improved. Allowing users to apply multiple filters simultaneously has enhanced usability.</p><p>A significant matter addressed involved notifications. A portion of devices failed to display system alerts. The issue originated from a synchronization error between the server and client registration tokens. After deploying a corrective update, synchronization now works reliably and all devices receive notifications as intended.</p><p>UI layout modifications were also made to improve clarity, and backend routines underwent minor corrections for better performance.</p><h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2><p>Current operations show improvement across all modules. With the notification defect resolved, overall system stability is now much stronger.</p>\\\"\"',NULL,NULL,'2025-11-20 21:48:00.000','6a8aa455-94f0-4e98-92e7-809c64adcfe4'),('ddba1ca6-8522-4af9-afa0-ad8d449761a2','? Daily Work Progress Report','\"\\\"<h1>? Daily Work Progress Report</h1><p><br></p><h3>? Introduction</h3><p>Today, I focused on strengthening the <strong>Employee Attendance Management</strong> module within <strong>Aby Dash</strong>. The goal was to streamline how employee attendance is recorded, tracked, and managed across the system.</p><h3>✅ Key Tasks Completed</h3><h4>? 1. Attendance Tracking Backend</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Developed and refined backend logic to securely record daily employee attendance.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured accurate logging for check-in and check-out times.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added validation to prevent duplicate or invalid attendance entries.</li></ol><h4>? 2. Attendance Status Management</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Implemented automated rules to categorize attendance records (Present, Absent, Late, or Missing).</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Improved how attendance data flows into dashboards and reports.</li><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Ensured the system responds in real time when attendance is submitted or updated.</li></ol><h4>? 3. Attendance Update &amp; Correction</h4><ol><li data-list=\\\\\\\"bullet\\\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\\\"ql-ui\\\\\\\" contenteditable=\\\\\\\"false\\\\\\\"></span>Added features allowing HR or